  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Distance Traveled in Six Minute Walk Test</measure>
    <time_frame>Three months</time_frame>
    <description>Relationship of the step count and distance measure of the LifeVest walk test in heart failure patients as compared to distance measure of medically supervised 6-minute walk test. Accuracy of activities, and body position in patients with heart failure as compared to patient diaries of activity and sleeping position.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
